Introduction

PRIKIL is a 5-member Japanese girl group under FNC Entertainment Japan formed through the reality show "Who Is Princess?".
They debuted with the single "SOMEBODY" on May 4, 2022.

On December 31, 2023, it was announced that Rinko and Uta‘s contract had been terminated and that they would no longer be able to perform due to personal reasons.
